    {
      "name": "Torchforger's Covenant",
      "description": "After unleashing Elemental Skill Dawnbearing Songbird or Elemental Burst Shadowless Reflection, other nearby party members will gain the Lightkeeper's Oath effect for 20s: For Geo DMG dealt to opponents, CRIT Rate increases by 5% and CRIT DMG increases by 10%.\n\nMoonsign: Ascendant Gleam \nParty members affected by the Lightkeeper's Oath effect have their Elemental Mastery increased by 50.",
